{"tid":1679722,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對應党鐵既戰略提議","createTime":"2019-10-28T11:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T15:50:32.000Z","uid":35823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ef196044754c7937be9add2c0bdd9055ae1b9a","tid":1679722,"uid":35823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"發夢發到今時今日<br />\n個人有提議，希望前線和大家可以集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n兒家一有咩事党鐵都會停宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n如果要繼續針党鐵，其實應該針對佢地既廣告，因為有幾個好處<br />\n<br />\n1. 重要收入來源, 同時影響落廣告既商戶，因為重整後又要再登，廣告日數又要再計<br />\n2. 不影響行車和市民，党鐵強行關閉另計<br />\n3. 唔計月台廣告，其實地面既廣告容易快閃，針對背景燈光同frame, 大量重造加重登廣告返需時<br />\n4. 相比入閘機，鏡頭，電視，党鐵行政負擔大<br />\n<br />\n我只係提議下，因為好似冇人針過廣告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但提醒大家，上星期睇住職員室出廿隻狗，但可以聲東擊西！"},{"pid":"3dcd56c6e4091c0021b63ace0b42be511386e7fc","tid":1679722,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:08:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6caeaa3ad32835ab3ba252e2f847f92515871c5a","tid":1679722,"uid":32454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528208fc9525baaaaf3407100ac72f4e3d7fa18c","tid":1679722,"uid":78074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"有諗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5371f6a09af5a54aa17b1b27e4d0d5713acf028c","tid":1679722,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"太天真了！依家停駛要理由？扑爆塊玻璃就可以即停"},{"pid":"d53ba909e65e90a2f720ff76b9e8a8b5bc01a98c","tid":1679722,"uid":35823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5371f6a09af5a54aa17b1b27e4d0d5713acf028c","tid":1679722,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"太天真了！依家停駛要理由？扑爆塊玻璃就可以即停"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:50:32.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊佢停唔停<br />\n<br />\n係點作出有效既攻擊破壞入閘機，票機，對党鐵經濟傷害低，但阻到大眾。相反，廣告就唔同"}]}